<h3>ManualDraw</h3>
<p class="muted">
    Lets someone scan a QR code next to the table, hold a button for a few seconds, and
    steer the ball with their phone's tilt. Whatever the table was drawing pauses while
    they're in control and resumes when they let go.
</p>

<form class="form-horizontal">

    <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label">{{ _('Enabled') }}</label>
        <div class="controls">
            <label class="checkbox">
                <input type="checkbox" data-bind="checked: settings.plugins.manualdraw.enabled">
                {{ _('Master switch — allow the QR page to take control') }}
            </label>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr>
    <h4>{{ _('Table bounds (mm)') }}</h4>
    <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label">{{ _('X range') }}</label>
        <div class="controls">
            <input type="number" class="input-mini" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.manualdraw.table_min_x"> &ndash;
            <input type="number" class="input-mini" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.manualdraw.table_max_x">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label">{{ _('Y range') }}</label>
        <div class="controls">
            <input type="number" class="input-mini" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.manualdraw.table_min_y"> &ndash;
            <input type="number" class="input-mini" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.manualdraw.table_max_y">
            <span class="help-block">{{ _('Defaults to the real 370x400mm bed. Manual jogs are clamped to this box.') }}</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr>
    <h4>{{ _('Control feel') }}</h4>
    <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label">{{ _('Max speed (mm/s)') }}</label>
        <div class="controls">
            <input type="number" min="1" class="input-mini" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.manualdraw.max_speed_mm_s">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label">{{ _('Jog feedrate') }}</label>
        <div class="controls">
            <input type="number" min="1" class="input-mini" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.manualdraw.jog_feedrate">
            <span class="help-block">{{ _('Keep well above Max speed x 60, or the feedrate itself becomes the limiter.') }}</span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label">{{ _('Dead zone (deg)') }}</label>
        <div class="controls">
            <input type="number" min="0" class="input-mini" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.manualdraw.dead_zone_deg">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label">{{ _('Max tilt (deg)') }}</label>
        <div class="controls">
            <input type="number" min="1" class="input-mini" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.manualdraw.max_tilt_deg">
            <span class="help-block">{{ _('Tilt at or beyond this angle from the calibrated center = full speed.') }}</span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label">{{ _('Hold to activate (s)') }}</label>
        <div class="controls">
            <input type="number" min="1" class="input-mini" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.manualdraw.hold_seconds">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="control-group">
        <label class="control-label">{{ _('Watchdog timeout (s)') }}</label>
        <div class="controls">
            <input type="number" min="1" class="input-mini" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.manualdraw.watchdog_timeout_seconds">
            <span class="help-block">{{ _('Auto-release control (and resume the paused draw) if the phone stops sending updates for this long.') }}</span>
        </div>
    </div>

</form>
